				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Bugbear vendor yells at the player when entering combat. If at least one of the players had impressed him, he wil look forward to the challange of fighting them. If they failed to impresse him, he will taunt them. If not of the players attempted to impress him, he will be existed for the bloodshed regardless."
